+
+You can now add a `systemId` to spawned actors to reference them anywhere in the system.
+
+```ts
+const machine = createMachine({
+  // ...
+  context: ({ spawn }) => ({
+    actorRef: spawn(
+      createMachine({
+        // ...
+      }),
+      { systemId: 'actorRef' }
+    )
+  })
+});
+```
